				<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The Lucidia Metaverse has made a detailed plan for the years 2023 to 2025 that shows how the platform will grow, change, and reach important milestones. The timeline shows that Lucidia wants to grow and change all the time, giving its users and investors new features and chances.</span></p><p> </p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Dates and Major Events:</span></p><p> </p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Q1 &#8211; Q2 | 2023:</span></p><p> </p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">NFT Tower Galleries Release</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Whitelist to get access to alpha</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The first PC alpha came out</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Token TGE Embryo DLC is now available</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Launch of tokens on the CEX and DEX Own building system</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">CG and CMC listing</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Major tier 1 CEX listing with blockchain</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Reach a market capitalization of $1 million between Q3 and Q4 of 2023:</span></p><p> </p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The CEX</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">What&#8217;s going on?</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Release of the NFT series II</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Shop for NFT upgrades in real life</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Alpha Train2Earn for mobile closed beta Open beta mobile Cross chain AI infrastructure</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The first LAN eSports event</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Reach a market value of $4 million between Q1 and Q2 of 2024:</span></p><p> </p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Integration of VR and the Land System</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">CEX listing</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Release of the Burn event NFT series 3</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Learn how to win the second e-sports tournament</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Your own NFT market</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Hybrid DAO democracy at the Digital World Film Festival</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Reach a market value of $10 million</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Q3 &#8211; Q4 | 2024:</span></p><p> </p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">CEX will list next</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Train2Earn beta launch</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">VOIP system for the virtual world music festival</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The fourth esports competition</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Update on virtual reality therapy with Brain AI NFT</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Job market for virtual reality on web3</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Reach $15 million capitalization</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Q1 &#8211; Q2 | 2025:</span></p><p> </p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Lucidia Metaverse 2.0: better graphics, ecosystems, artificial intelligence</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Protocols for decentralized identity</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Lucidia University is an online school.</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Lucidia Wallet: mobile app for $</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">LUCID management</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Esports have grown, with more tournaments and prizes.</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Lucidia Labs: space for developers</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">NFTs, merchandise, and other major brand partnerships</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">DAO implementation: community-driven decisions</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Lucid Experience: immersive event series</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The roadmap shows that Lucidia Metaverses is committed to making a platform that pushes the limits of virtual experiences and wants to be a leader in the rapidly growing metaverse landscape.</span></p>					</div>
